<div id="left-store">
    <div class="warning">
        Next SoundCloud is now the new SoundCloud, for everyone. 
Take advantage of the great new features. Search & Explore to find original music & audio you'll love.

Play a sound and enjoy Continuous Play while you explore the rest of SoundCloud.

Use Related Sounds to easily discover more sounds you'll want to hear.

And repost sounds and sets to share them from your stream.
    </div>

<% @articles.each do |article| %>
    <div id="article">
        <div id="the-author">
          <img src="<%= article.user.avatar.url %>">
        </div>
        <div id="onearticle">
        <div class="the-title">
          <%= article.title %>
          <div class="edit">

            <a href="" class="button">Add To Journal</a>
            <%= link_to 'Destroy', article, :class => "negative button cross", method: :delete, data: { confirm: 'Are you sure?' } %>

          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="content">

            <%= truncate(article.content , :length => 140) %>

        </div>
    </div>
    </div>

<% end %>  
</div>
<div id="right-store">
    <div class="notice">
        <h1>
            People of the world
        </h1>
Spread the words, connect the nodes, by sharing them and following them on journals.
</div>
</div>


<%= link_to 'New Article', new_article_path %>
